\c 4
\s1 Nebuchadnezzar Confesses God’s Kingdom
\m 
\v 1 King \w Nebuchadnezzar|strong="H5020"\w*,
\b
\m \w To|strong="H1934"\w* \w the|strong="H5020"\w* people \w of|strong="H1005"\w* every nation \w and|strong="H1005"\w* language who dwell \w in|strong="H1965"\w* all \w the|strong="H5020"\w* earth:
\b
\m May \w your|strong="H5020"\w* prosperity \w be|strong="H1934"\w* multiplied.
\v 2 I am pleased \w to|strong="H5922"\w* declare \w the|strong="H5922"\w* signs \w and|strong="H1763"\w* wonders \w that|strong="H1763"\w* \w the|strong="H5922"\w* Most High God has performed \w for|strong="H5922"\w* \w me|strong="H5922"\w*.
