\s1 Nebuchadnezzar’s Dream of a Great Tree
\b
\m 
\v 4 I, Nebuchadnezzar, was at ease \w in|strong="H5954"\w* my house \w and|strong="H2493"\w* flourishing \w in|strong="H5954"\w* my palace.
