\q2 \w and|strong="H8065"\w* gives it \w to|strong="H8065"\w* \w whom|strong="H1768"\w* \w He|strong="H1768"\w* wishes,
\q2 setting over it \w the|strong="H3606"\w* lowliest \w of|strong="H1768"\w* men.’
\b
\m 
\v 18 \w This|strong="H3606"\w* \w is|strong="H3606"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* dream \w that|strong="H3606"\w* I, King Nebuchadnezzar, saw. Now, Belteshazzar, tell me \w the|strong="H3606"\w* interpretation, \w because|strong="H3606"\w* \w none|strong="H3606"\w* \w of|strong="H3606"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* wise men \w of|strong="H3606"\w* my kingdom can interpret \w it|strong="H6853"\w* \w for|strong="H4203"\w* me. \w But|strong="H3606"\w* you are able, \w because|strong="H3606"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* spirit \w of|strong="H3606"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* holy gods \w is|strong="H3606"\w* \w in|strong="H1753"\w* you.”
\s1 Daniel Interprets the Second Dream
\b
\m 
\v 19 \w For|strong="H1768"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* time, Daniel, \w who|strong="H1768"\w* \w was|strong="H4430"\w* \w also|strong="H4430"\w* known \w as|strong="H1768"\w* Belteshazzar, \w was|strong="H4430"\w* perplexed, \w and|strong="H4430"\w* \w his|strong="H1768"\w* thoughts alarmed him.
\b
\m \w So|strong="H1768"\w* \w the|strong="H1768"\w* \w king|strong="H4430"\w* said, “Belteshazzar, \w do|strong="H8065"\w* not let \w the|strong="H1768"\w* dream \w or|strong="H4430"\w* its interpretation alarm \w you|strong="H1768"\w*.”
\b
\m “\w My|strong="H1768"\w* lord,” replied Belteshazzar, “may \w the|strong="H1768"\w* dream apply \w to|strong="H4430"\w* \w those|strong="H1768"\w* \w who|strong="H1768"\w* hate \w you|strong="H1768"\w*, \w and|strong="H4430"\w* its interpretation \w to|strong="H4430"\w* \w your|strong="H1768"\w* enemies!
\b
\m 
\v 20 \w The|strong="H5922"\w* tree \w you|strong="H1768"\w* \w saw|strong="H2370"\w* \w that|strong="H1768"\w* grew large \w and|strong="H6523"\w* strong, \w whose|strong="H1768"\w* top reached \w the|strong="H5922"\w* \w sky|strong="H8065"\w* \w and|strong="H6523"\w* \w was|strong="H4430"\w* visible \w to|strong="H5922"\w* all \w the|strong="H5922"\w* earth,
\v 21 \w whose|strong="H1768"\w* foliage \w was|strong="H4430"\w* beautiful \w and|strong="H4430"\w* \w whose|strong="H1768"\w* fruit \w was|strong="H4430"\w* abundant, providing food \w for|strong="H5922"\w* all, under \w which|strong="H1768"\w* \w the|strong="H5922"\w* beasts \w of|strong="H4430"\w* \w the|strong="H5922"\w* field lived, \w and|strong="H4430"\w* \w in|strong="H5922"\w* \w whose|strong="H1768"\w* branches \w the|strong="H5922"\w* birds \w of|strong="H4430"\w* \w the|strong="H5922"\w* air nested—
\v 22 \w you|strong="H1768"\w*, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* king, \w are|strong="H1768"\w* \w that|strong="H1768"\w* tree! \w For|strong="H5922"\w* \w you|strong="H1768"\w* \w have|strong="H1934"\w* become great \w and|strong="H4437"\w* strong; \w your|strong="H1768"\w* greatness \w has|strong="H1768"\w* grown \w to|strong="H5922"\w* reach \w the|strong="H5922"\w* \w sky|strong="H8065"\w*, \w and|strong="H4437"\w* \w your|strong="H1768"\w* dominion extends \w to|strong="H5922"\w* \w the|strong="H5922"\w* ends \w of|strong="H4481"\w* \w the|strong="H5922"\w* earth.
\b
\m 
\v 23 \w And|strong="H4437"\w* \w you|strong="H1768"\w*, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* king, saw \w a|strong="H3068"\w* watcher, \w a|strong="H3068"\w* holy one, coming down \w from|strong="H4481"\w* \w heaven|strong="H8065"\w* \w and|strong="H4437"\w* saying:
\b
\q1 ‘Cut down \w the|strong="H4481"\w* tree \w and|strong="H4437"\w* destroy \w it|strong="H4481"\w*,
\q2 \w but|strong="H4481"\w* \w leave|strong="H7662"\w* \w the|strong="H4481"\w* \w stump|strong="H6136"\w* with \w its|strong="H3046"\w* \w roots|strong="H8330"\w* \w in|strong="H4437"\w* \w the|strong="H4481"\w* ground,
\q1 \w and|strong="H4437"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* band \w of|strong="H4481"\w* iron \w and|strong="H4437"\w* bronze around \w it|strong="H4481"\w*,
\q2 \w in|strong="H4437"\w* \w the|strong="H4481"\w* tender grass \w of|strong="H4481"\w* \w the|strong="H4481"\w* field.
\b
\q1 Let \w him|strong="H4481"\w* be drenched with \w the|strong="H4481"\w* dew \w of|strong="H4481"\w* \w heaven|strong="H8065"\w*,
\q2 \w and|strong="H4437"\w* graze with \w the|strong="H4481"\w* beasts \w of|strong="H4481"\w* \w the|strong="H4481"\w* field
\q2 till seven times pass \w him|strong="H4481"\w* \w by|strong="H4481"\w*.’
\b
\m 
\v 24 \w This|strong="H5922"\w* is \w the|strong="H5922"\w* interpretation, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* \w king|strong="H4430"\w*, \w and|strong="H4430"\w* \w this|strong="H5922"\w* is \w the|strong="H5922"\w* decree \w that|strong="H2006"\w* \w the|strong="H5922"\w* Most High \w has|strong="H4430"\w* issued \w against|strong="H5922"\w* \w my|strong="H5922"\w* lord \w the|strong="H5922"\w* \w king|strong="H4430"\w*:
\b
\m 
\v 25 \w You|strong="H5922"\w* \w will|strong="H4430"\w* be driven away from mankind, \w and|strong="H4430"\w* \w your|strong="H5020"\w* dwelling \w will|strong="H4430"\w* be \w with|strong="H5922"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* beasts \w of|strong="H4430"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* field. \w You|strong="H5922"\w* \w will|strong="H4430"\w* feed \w on|strong="H5922"\w* grass like \w an|strong="H3606"\w* ox \w and|strong="H4430"\w* be drenched \w with|strong="H5922"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* dew \w of|strong="H4430"\w* heaven, \w and|strong="H4430"\w* seven times \w shall|strong="H3606"\w* pass \w you|strong="H5922"\w* by, until \w you|strong="H5922"\w* acknowledge \w that|strong="H3606"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* Most High rules \w over|strong="H5922"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* kingdom \w of|strong="H4430"\w* mankind \w and|strong="H4430"\w* gives \w it|strong="H5922"\w* \w to|strong="H5922"\w* whom \w He|strong="H5020"\w* wishes.
\b
\m 
\v 26 \w As|strong="H1768"\w* \w for|strong="H5922"\w* \w the|strong="H5922"\w* command \w to|strong="H5922"\w* leave \w the|strong="H5922"\w* stump \w of|strong="H4437"\w* \w the|strong="H5922"\w* tree \w with|strong="H5922"\w* its roots, \w your|strong="H1768"\w* \w kingdom|strong="H4437"\w* \w will|strong="H1768"\w* \w be|strong="H1934"\w* restored \w to|strong="H5922"\w* \w you|strong="H1768"\w* \w as|strong="H1768"\w* \w soon|strong="H1768"\w* \w as|strong="H1768"\w* \w you|strong="H1768"\w* acknowledge \w that|strong="H1768"\w* Heaven rules.
\v 27 Therefore, may \w my|strong="H1768"\w* advice \w be|strong="H3809"\w* pleasing \w to|strong="H4430"\w* \w you|strong="H1768"\w*, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* \w king|strong="H4430"\w*. Break away \w from|strong="H1768"\w* \w your|strong="H1768"\w* sins by doing \w what|strong="H1768"\w* \w is|strong="H1768"\w* right, \w and|strong="H6032"\w* \w from|strong="H1768"\w* \w your|strong="H1768"\w* iniquities by showing mercy \w to|strong="H4430"\w* \w the|strong="H1768"\w* oppressed. Perhaps \w there|strong="H1768"\w* \w will|strong="H1768"\w* \w be|strong="H3809"\w* \w an|strong="H4437"\w* extension \w of|strong="H1005"\w* \w your|strong="H1768"\w* prosperity.”
\s1 The Second Dream Fulfilled
\b
\m 
\v 28 All \w this|strong="H4481"\w* happened \w to|strong="H5308"\w* \w King|strong="H4430"\w* \w Nebuchadnezzar|strong="H5020"\w*.
\v 29 Twelve months later, \w as|strong="H6211"\w* \w he|strong="H1768"\w* \w was|strong="H2423"\w* walking \w on|strong="H5922"\w* \w the|strong="H5922"\w* roof \w of|strong="H4481"\w* \w the|strong="H5922"\w* \w royal|strong="H4437"\w* palace \w of|strong="H4481"\w* Babylon,
\v 30 \w the|strong="H5922"\w* king exclaimed, “\w Is|strong="H1768"\w* \w this|strong="H5922"\w* not Babylon \w the|strong="H5922"\w* \w Great|strong="H7236"\w*, \w which|strong="H1768"\w* \w I|strong="H4481"\w* myself \w have|strong="H1768"\w* built \w by|strong="H4481"\w* \w the|strong="H5922"\w* might \w of|strong="H4481"\w* \w my|strong="H5922"\w* power \w as|strong="H6211"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* royal residence \w and|strong="H7236"\w* \w for|strong="H5922"\w* \w the|strong="H5922"\w* glory \w of|strong="H4481"\w* \w my|strong="H5922"\w* majesty?”
\b
\m 
\v 31 While \w the|strong="H5922"\w* words \w were|strong="H1768"\w* still \w in|strong="H5922"\w* \w the|strong="H5922"\w* king’s mouth, \w a|strong="H3068"\w* voice \w came|strong="H1768"\w* \w from|strong="H1768"\w* \w heaven|strong="H8065"\w*: “\w It|strong="H5922"\w* \w is|strong="H1768"\w* decreed \w to|strong="H5922"\w* \w you|strong="H1768"\w*, King \w Nebuchadnezzar|strong="H5020"\w*, \w that|strong="H1768"\w* \w the|strong="H5922"\w* \w kingdom|strong="H4437"\w* \w has|strong="H1768"\w* departed \w from|strong="H1768"\w* \w you|strong="H1768"\w*.
\v 32 \w You|strong="H1768"\w* \w will|strong="H6634"\w* \w be|strong="H3809"\w* driven away \w from|strong="H1768"\w* mankind \w to|strong="H2429"\w* \w live|strong="H1753"\w* \w with|strong="H5648"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* beasts \w of|strong="H1768"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* field, \w and|strong="H8065"\w* \w you|strong="H1768"\w* \w will|strong="H6634"\w* feed on grass like \w an|strong="H5648"\w* ox. \w And|strong="H8065"\w* seven times \w will|strong="H6634"\w* \w pass|strong="H3809"\w* \w you|strong="H1768"\w* by, until \w you|strong="H1768"\w* acknowledge \w that|strong="H1768"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* \w Most|strong="H2429"\w* High rules over \w the|strong="H3606"\w* kingdom \w of|strong="H1768"\w* mankind \w and|strong="H8065"\w* gives it \w to|strong="H2429"\w* \w whom|strong="H1768"\w* \w He|strong="H1768"\w* \w wishes|strong="H6634"\w*.”
\b
\m 
\v 33 At \w that|strong="H5922"\w* moment \w the|strong="H5922"\w* sentence \w against|strong="H5922"\w* Nebuchadnezzar \w was|strong="H2122"\w* fulfilled. He \w was|strong="H2122"\w* driven away \w from|strong="H3367"\w* mankind. He ate grass like \w an|strong="H4437"\w* ox, \w and|strong="H4437"\w* \w his|strong="H5922"\w* body \w was|strong="H2122"\w* drenched \w with|strong="H5922"\w* \w the|strong="H5922"\w* dew \w of|strong="H4437"\w* heaven, until \w his|strong="H5922"\w* hair grew like \w the|strong="H5922"\w* feathers \w of|strong="H4437"\w* \w an|strong="H4437"\w* eagle \w and|strong="H4437"\w* \w his|strong="H5922"\w* nails like \w the|strong="H5922"\w* claws \w of|strong="H4437"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* bird.
\s1 Nebuchadnezzar Restored
\b
\m 
\v 34 \w But|strong="H3606"\w* at \w the|strong="H3606"\w* end \w of|strong="H4430"\w* \w those|strong="H8214"\w* days \w I|strong="H1768"\w*, \w Nebuchadnezzar|strong="H5020"\w*, looked \w up|strong="H7313"\w* \w to|strong="H3202"\w* \w heaven|strong="H8065"\w*, \w and|strong="H4430"\w* \w my|strong="H1768"\w* sanity \w was|strong="H4430"\w* restored \w to|strong="H3202"\w* me. \w Then|strong="H1768"\w* \w I|strong="H1768"\w* \w praised|strong="H7624"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* Most High, \w and|strong="H4430"\w* \w I|strong="H1768"\w* \w honored|strong="H1922"\w* \w and|strong="H4430"\w* \w glorified|strong="H1922"\w* Him \w who|strong="H1768"\w* lives forever:
\b
\q1 “\w For|strong="H1768"\w* \w His|strong="H1768"\w* dominion \w is|strong="H1768"\w* \w an|strong="H3606"\w* everlasting dominion,
\q2 \w and|strong="H4430"\w* \w His|strong="H1768"\w* kingdom endures \w from|strong="H1768"\w* generation \w to|strong="H3202"\w* generation.
\q1 
\v 35 All the peoples of the earth
\q2 are counted as nothing,
\q1 and He does as He pleases
\q2 with the army of heaven
\q2 and the peoples of the earth.
\q1 There is no one who can restrain His hand
\q2 or say to Him, ‘What have You done?’”
\b
\m 
\v 36 At the same time my sanity was restored, my honor and splendor returned to me for the glory of my kingdom. My advisers and nobles sought me out, and I was restored to my throne, and surpassing greatness was added to me.
\v 37 Now I, Nebuchadnezzar, praise and exalt and glorify the King of heaven, for all His works are true and all His ways are just. And He is able to humble those who walk in pride.
\c 5
\s1 Belshazzar’s Feast
\m 
\v 1 Later, \f + \fr 5:1 \ft Aramaic does not include Later. Some translators include Many years later to account for the time elapsed, probably about 30 years, since the previous chapter.\f* \w King|strong="H4430"\w* \w Belshazzar|strong="H1113"\w* \w held|strong="H5648"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w great|strong="H7229"\w* \w feast|strong="H3900"\w* \w for|strong="H6903"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* thousand \w of|strong="H4430"\w* his \w nobles|strong="H7261"\w*, \w and|strong="H4430"\w* \w he|strong="H6903"\w* \w drank|strong="H8355"\w* \w wine|strong="H2562"\w* \w with|strong="H5648"\w* them.
