\v 9 Therefore \w King|strong="H4430"\w* Darius \w signed|strong="H7560"\w* \w the|strong="H1768"\w* \w written|strong="H7560"\w* \w decree|strong="H1882"\w*.
\s1 Daniel in the Lions’ Den
\b
\m 
\v 10 \w Now|strong="H4430"\w* when Daniel learned \w that|strong="H3606"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* \w document|strong="H3792"\w* \w had|strong="H4430"\w* been \w signed|strong="H7560"\w*, \w he|strong="H6903"\w* went into \w his|strong="H3606"\w* house, where \w the|strong="H3606"\w* windows \w of|strong="H4430"\w* \w his|strong="H3606"\w* upper room opened toward Jerusalem, \w and|strong="H4430"\w* three times \w a|strong="H3068"\w* day \w he|strong="H6903"\w* got down on \w his|strong="H3606"\w* knees, prayed, \w and|strong="H4430"\w* gave thanks \w to|strong="H1868"\w* \w his|strong="H3606"\w* God, \w just|strong="H6903"\w* \w as|strong="H3606"\w* \w he|strong="H6903"\w* \w had|strong="H4430"\w* done \w before|strong="H6903"\w*.
\v 11 \w Then|strong="H6903"\w* \w these|strong="H1836"\w* men \w went|strong="H5954"\w* \w as|strong="H3606"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* group \w and|strong="H1005"\w* found \w Daniel|strong="H1841"\w* petitioning \w and|strong="H1005"\w* imploring \w his|strong="H5922"\w* God.
\v 12 So they approached \w the|strong="H6925"\w* king \w and|strong="H1841"\w* \w asked|strong="H1156"\w* about \w his|strong="H6925"\w* royal decree: “Did you not sign \w a|strong="H3068"\w* decree \w that|strong="H1400"\w* \w for|strong="H1156"\w* thirty days any \w man|strong="H1400"\w* who petitions any god or \w man|strong="H1400"\w* except you, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* king, will \w be|strong="H1841"\w* thrown into \w the|strong="H6925"\w* den \w of|strong="H6925"\w* lions?”
